Phần 1: Giới thiệu Đồ án¶

  • Bnh tim mch l cc tnh trng lin quan n sc khe ca tri tim, s hot ng ca cc mch mu gy suy yu kh nng lm vic ca tim. Cc bnh tim mch bao gm: cc bnh mch mu nh bnh ng mch vnh, bnh c tim, lon nhp tim v suy tim.
  • Bnh tim mch c th xy ra mi tui, gii tnh, ngh nghip. Bnh khng th cha khi hon ton, i hi s iu tr v theo di cn thn (thm ch l sut i), tn km nhiu chi ph.
  • Theo T chc Y t Th gii, hng nm c n hn 17 triu ngi t vong v bnh tim mch. Con s ny cho thy mc ph bin ca cc bnh l v tim l rt cao. V vy nn nhm em quyt nh chn ch ny n cui k cho mn "Nhp mn lp trnh Python cho phn tch".

Câu hỏi Nghiên cứu chung¶

  • Ht thuc l c l nguyn nhn gy ra bnh tim hay khng?
  • Sc khe hay tui c lm tng nguy c b bnh tim khng?
  • Sc khe tinh thn v th cht c nh hng ti vic b bnh tim hay khng?
  • Tm hiu cc bnh nn v cc ch s c th lm nh hng ti vic b bnh tim hay khng.
  • v.v (Cn cp nht thm)

  • Bin phn loi (nh tnh): HeartDisease, Smoking, AlcoholDrinking, Stroke, DiffWalking, Sex, AgeCategory, Diabetic, PhysicalActivity, GenHealth, Asthma, KidneyDisease, SkinCancer
  • Bin s (nh lng): BMI, PhysicalHealth, MentalHealth, SleepTime

In [57]:
def Draw_pie_chart(name_feature):

    fig,axes = plt.subplots(1,2,figsize=(15,8))
    labels = data[name_feature].unique()
    textprops = {"fontsize":15}

    axes[0].pie(data[data.HeartDisease=="No"][name_feature].value_counts(), labels=labels,autopct='%1.1f%%',textprops =textprops)
    axes[0].set_title('No Heart Disease',fontsize=15)
    axes[1].pie(data[data.HeartDisease=="Yes"][name_feature].value_counts(), labels=labels,autopct='%1.1f%%',textprops =textprops)
    axes[1].set_title('Yes Heart Disease',fontsize=15)

    plt.legend(title = name_feature, fontsize=15, title_fontsize=15)
    plt.show()
